The beehoon is really tasty. Very unique taste compared to the other economical beehoon.
Beehoon, egg, chicken wing and egg $3.50. porridge $1. The queue is worth it.
Bee hoon really lives up to expectation. Very traditional taste and chicken wing is a must try. Expect a long line but itâ€™s worth it.
This is my favourite breakfast option in Tanglin Halt market. Very yummy and affordable!

My all-time favourite breakfast bee hoon stall. Auntie at the stall is super friendly. The bee hoon is moist and fragrant. I love the fried noodles too! It's economical and delicious! But most of the time, be ready to queue. The queue moves really fast though.
